text: Ronni Moesgaard Bagge (born October 5, 1984 in Grædstrup) is a Danish professional football player who currently plays for the Danish Superliga club Vejle Boldklub. ==External links== * Vejle Boldklub profile Category:1984 births Category:Danish footballers Category:Living people Category:Vejle Boldklub players Category:Thisted FC players Category:Association football midfielders
